Package: homerviz
Title: Visualization of HOMER Known Motif Discovery Results
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Author", "Huan Yang", email = "hyang333@wisc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Parses and visualizes HOMER known motif discovery results. 
    Provides an S4 class 'HomerData' to store parsed results and functions 
    to create publication-quality ComplexHeatmap visualizations including 
    motif rank, transcription factor names, motif logos, significance 
    (-log P-value), and target percentage bar plots.
